'''耶穌一生'''{{noteTag|也称作 '''''Sefer Toledot Yeshu''''', '''''Toldoth Yechu''''', '''''Sepher Toldos Jeschu'''''等}} (""תולדות ישו Toledot Yeshu，"The Biography of Jesus") 是一本[[諧仿|諧仿]][[耶稣|耶稣]]生世的[[犹太|犹太]][[亚拉姆文|亚拉姆文]]文献，是从[[反基督教|反基督教]]观点出发的[[犹太|犹太]]版本的[[耶稣|耶稣]]生平<ref name="voorst">{{cite book
|title=Jesus Outside the New Testament: A Introduction to the Ancient Evidence
|first=Robert E.
|last=Van Voorst
|pages=pp 122f
|year=2000
|publisher=Wm. B. Eerdmans Publishing
|isbn=0802843689}}</ref>。它也被基督徒称作[[反福音|反福音]]<ref name="voorst" />。这本书的题目翻译成英语有：'''Book of the Life of Jesus'''<ref name=voorst/>、'''Generations of Jesus'''<ref name=tolan>{{cite book
|title=Saracens: Islam in the Medieval European Imagination
|first=John Victor
|last=Tolan
|pages=17f
|publisher=Columbia University Press
|location=New York
|year=2002
|isbn=0231123329}}</ref>或者'''The Life of Jesus'''<ref name="schafer">{{cite book
|title=Mirror of His Beauty: Feminine Images of God from the Bible to the Early Kabbalah
|first=Peter
|last=Schäfer
|pages=pp 211f
|year=2002
|publisher=Princeton University Press
|isbn=0691090688}}</ref>。《耶稣一生》认为耶稣“放肆”<ref name="voorst" />，并将耶稣描述為一个会[[魔法|魔法]]、羞辱而死的[[私生子|私生子]]。<ref name="webster">{{cite book
|title=Secret Societies and Subversive Movements
|first=Nesta H.
|last=Webster
|pages= pp 21f
|year=2000
|publisher=Book Tree
|isbn=1585090921}}</ref>
主要观点就是耶稣是一个[[骗子|骗子]]和[[异教徒|异教徒]]<ref>Van Voorst. p. 127</ref>。

==历史==
这本书中的主要内容来源于流传的口头传说，主要收入的内容在古代晚期（4世纪早期或者6世纪左右）<ref name="mass">{{cite book
|title=The Cambridge Companion to the Age of Justinian
|first=Michael
|last=Maas
|pages=pg 406
|year=2005
|publisher=Cambridge University Press
|isbn=0521817463}}</ref>）或者中世纪早期<ref name=voorst/>。这本书从九世纪广泛流传于[[欧洲|欧洲]]和[[中东|中东]]地区；<ref name="voorst" /> , 在''De Iudaicis Superstitionibus''这本书裡，<ref name=schafer/>[[天主教里昂总教区|天主教里昂总教区]]的[[Agobard|Agobard]]在826年曾经证实有这本书存在。<ref name=voorst/> 

原始版本是[[亚拉姆语|亚拉姆语]]，后来有了修订版的[[希伯来语|希伯来语]]版本，晚期版本使用[[犹太-波斯语|犹太-波斯语]]和[[阿拉伯语|阿拉伯语]]、[[意第绪语|意第绪语]]和[[拉地诺语|拉地诺语]]（犹太-西班牙语）<ref name=gero>{{cite journal
 |last = Gero
 |first = Stephan
 |date = 1988
 |title = Apocraphyl Gospels: A Survey
 |journal = Aufsteig UN Niedergang Der Romischen Welt
 |volume = Teil II
 |issue = Band 25 (5 teilband)
 |pages = pp 3391f
 |id = ISBN 3110018853
 |url = http://books.google.com/books?vid=ISBN3110018853&id=lF3DXBA2YlcC&pg=PT374&lpg=PT374&dq=Toldoth+Yeshu&sig=3JV5E5biUyt_BhYw6DrzUztl4WY#PPT374,M1
 |language = de,en
 |access-date = 2009-05-14
 |archive-date = 2014-07-17
 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140717101758/http://books.google.com/books?vid=ISBN3110018853&id=lF3DXBA2YlcC&pg=PT374&lpg=PT374&dq=Toldoth+Yeshu&sig=3JV5E5biUyt_BhYw6DrzUztl4WY#PPT374,M1
 |dead-url = no
 }}</ref>。这本书在基督教世纪一直闻所未闻，直到13世纪末期它才由[[道明会|道明会]][[修道士|修道士]][[雷蒙·马丁|雷蒙·马丁]]翻译成[[拉丁语|拉丁语]]。<ref name=webster/>
直到最近学者們才对它有一点关注，“很有可能是与它令人讨厌的内容和吸引目光的定位”有关。<ref name=voorst/>

